# Build governance

- Follow `BUILD.md` phases **in order**. Do not skip acceptance gates or loosen them to pass.
- Before starting work: read `status.md` for current phase and blockers.
- After completing a gate: update `status.md` and, if `[REVIEW]`, prepare the artifact for `handoff.md`.
- Specs live in `docs/`. Agent prompts live in `agents/`. Skills live in `.cursor/skills/`.
- When Claude reviews and Cursor implements (or vice versa), use `handoff.md` as the single handoff contract.
- Claude may drop files at repo root — copy to target paths, merge `status2.md`/`handoff2.md` into canonical files, archive root copies in `others/`.
- Never let the LLM compute CRS, edge, or EV. Never add execution features.
